| dead-url=  no
}}</ref> 按收入结算，杰尼亚是全球最大的时尚男装品牌。<ref>[http://www.businessoffashion.com/2014/04/ermenegildo-zegna-fashions-family-giant.html Ermenegildo Zegna: Fashion’s Family Giant] {{Wayback|url=http://www.businessoffashion.com/2014/04/ermenegildo-zegna-fashions-family-giant.html |date=20150227105718 }}, businessoffashion.com 29 April 2014</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billionaire.com/mens-fashion/1223/gildo-zegna-a-casual-conversation#content-page-2 |publisher=Billionaire.com |accessdate=January 4, 2015 |title=Gildo Zegna: A Casual Conversation |author=Christian Barker |date=November 18, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624082313/http://www.billionaire.com/mens-fashion/1223/gildo-zegna-a-casual-conversation#content-page-2 |archive-date=2016-06-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>  [[亚历山德罗·萨托利|亚历山德罗·萨托利]]担任各品牌部门的创意总监。<ref>businessoffashion.com [http://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/bof-exclusive/bof-exclusive-zegna-to-tap-alessandro-sartori Zegna to tap Alessandro Sartori] {{Wayback|url=http://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/bof-exclusive/bof-exclusive-zegna-to-tap-alessandro-sartori |date=20180927044419 }}</ref>2018年8月28日Zegna收購Thom Browne85%股權。而餘下的15%股權則繼續由Thom Browne持有。

==創意總監==

Alessandro Sartori負責品牌各個部門的創意指導。他曾在2003年至2011年擔任創意總監，五年後回到品牌，於2016年6月被任命為藝術總監。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://wwd.com/menswear-news/mens-fashion/alessandro-sartori-returns-ermenegildo-zegna-10340961/|title=Ermenegildo Zegna Confirms Alessandro Sartori Return|last=|first=|date=|website=wwd.com|language=en-us|access-date=2019-09-12|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226105541/https://wwd.com/menswear-news/mens-fashion/alessandro-sartori-returns-ermenegildo-zegna-10340961/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/alessandro-sartori-named-ermenegildo-zegna-862538|title=Alessandro Sartori Named Ermenegildo Zegna Artistic Director|last=|first=|date=|website=www.hollywoodreporter.com|language=en-us|access-date=2019-09-12|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212024503/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/alessandro-sartori-named-ermenegildo-zegna-862538|dead-url=no}}</ref>

此前，Stefano Pilati曾擔任Ermenegildo Zegna Couture的設計主管三年。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.elle.com/fashion/news/a33757/stefano-pilati-exits-ermenegildo-zegna-couture/|title=Stefano Pilati To Exit Ermenegildo Zegna Couture|last=|first=|date=|website=www.elle.com|language=en-us|access-date=|archive-date=2020-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731053820/https://www.elle.com/fashion/news/a33757/stefano-pilati-exits-ermenegildo-zegna-couture/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 從2011年到2014年，Paul Surridge是Z Zegna的創意總監。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/paul-surridge-exit-roberto-cavalli-1203088689//|title=Paul Surridge Said to Exit Roberto Cavalli|last=|first=|date=|website=www.elle.com|language=en-us|access-date=|archive-date=2020-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200817234922/https://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/paul-surridge-exit-roberto-cavalli-1203088689/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==公司管理==

杰尼亚現在由杰尼亚家庭的第三代人管理，並仍然由家族所有。 Ermenegildo（Gildo）Zegna目前是首席執行官； 他的堂兄Paolo Zegna是該公司的董事長； 安娜·傑尼亞（Anna Zegna）是杰尼亚基金會的總裁。 埃梅內吉爾多的兒子安傑洛是名譽主席。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.vanityfair.com/culture/2010/06/zegna-spotlight-201006|title=Matt Tyrnauer and Wayne Maser spotlight Italy’s Zegna family, marking a century at the heart of men’s fashion.|last=|first=|date=|website=www.biography.com|language=en-us|access-date=|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130084959/https://www.vanityfair.com/culture/2010/06/zegna-spotlight-201006|dead-url=no}}</ref>

